<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="81.0">“It never occurred to him that I was actually Dr. Hopkins and this was my office,” she recalled. “The likelihood is, he took an educated guess and on this campus, I’m more likely to be the cleaner than be the professor.”</p>
        
    
