    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/uprooted">Uprooted</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/uprooted-documentary-christopher-newport-university-black-neighborhoods">
                                    “Uprooted” Explores How University Expansion and Eminent Domain Led to Black Land Loss
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Watch this examination of a Black community’s decadeslong battle to hold onto their land as city officials wielded eminent domain.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <span class="name">Brandi Kellam</span>, <span class="name">Christopher Tyree</span> and <span class="name">Louis Hansen</span>, <a href="https://vcij.org/">Virginia Center for Investigative Journalism at WHRO</a>, and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/lisa-riordan-seville">Lisa Riordan Seville</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/mauricio-rodriguez-pons">Mauricio Rodríguez Pons</a>, ProPublica,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2023-12-09EST06:00">Dec. 9, 2023, 6 a.m. EST</time>
        </p>

                <p class="story-card__unit">Local Reporting Network</p>
            </div>
</div>
                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    

                    
                    
    
        <div class="lead-art">
            <a class="aspect-3-2" href="https://www.propublica.org/article/these-virginia-universities-expanded-by-displacing-black-residents">
                <img
                    alt=""
                    src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%27http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%27%20width%3D%273%27%20height%3D%272%27%20style%3D%27background%3Atransparent%27%2F%3E"
                    srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230907-Tiernan-Eminent-Domain_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=267&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=0e843de031dfe20f2d26553d8301af7b 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230907-Tiernan-Eminent-Domain_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=533&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=76ad93971267dd4b35fd5f6670673a87 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230907-Tiernan-Eminent-Domain_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=800&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=1911fc417b74152d0e459c1b9be3dc5b 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230907-Tiernan-Eminent-Domain_preview_maxWidth_3000_maxHeight_3000_ppi_72_embedColorProfile_true_quality_95.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1067&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=a53b11f50da3c23a85b00581959d8951 1600w"
                    width="400"
                    height="267"
                    loading="lazy"
                    js-autosizes
                />
            </a>
        </div>
    
    <div class="story-card__description">
                        <a class="story-card__series" href="https://www.propublica.org/series/uprooted">Uprooted</a>
        
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
